Class OAuthAuthorizationData

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class OAuthAuthorizationData
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This bean represents a resource owner authorization challenge. Typically, an HTML view will be returned to a resource owner who will authorize or deny the third-party consumer
